  script: .github/scripts/sync_to_drive.py (193 linhas)
  auth: OAuth refresh token (GOOGLE_REFRESH_TOKEN + CLIENT_ID + CLIENT_SECRET)
  comportamento: upsert por nome+pasta no Drive, idempotente
